    </section>
</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>'Lock In': A Cop Story For Robot Lovers, A Robot Story For Cop Lovers</b>   <b data-is-speakable>John Scalzi's new <em>Lock In</em> is a successful genre mashup that balances the needs of a police procedural (dead body, damaged detective) with those of a science fiction yarn (hard-core world building).</b>
</div>
